      <br>• All-weather operation (rain or shine)
      <br>• Higher lifting capacities (up to 16 tons)
      <br>• Lower upfront cost (vs. equivalent electric)
      <br>• No charging downtime (continuous operation)
      <br>• Outdoor operation (no emissions concern)</p>

